#. translators: 1: voter display name, 2: site name, 3: closing date, 4: yes URL, 5: no URL
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:311
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"The %2$s community has opened a vote to remove a member. The vote closes on "
"%3$s.\n"
"\n"
"Cast your vote:\n"
"\n"
"Vote YES (remove): %4$s\n"
"\n"
"Vote NO (keep):    %5$s\n"
"\n"
"A majority of active members (more than 50%%) must vote yes for the removal "
"to proceed. You can change your vote by clicking the other link before the "
"deadline.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Hoi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"De %2$s-community heeft een stemming geopend om een lid te verwijderen. De "
"stemming sluit op %3$s.\n"
"\n"
"Breng je stem uit:\n"
"\n"
"Stem JA (verwijderen): %4$s\n"
"\n"
"Stem NEE (behouden):    %5$s\n"
"\n"
"Een meerderheid van de actieve leden (meer dan 50%%) moet ja stemmen voordat "
"de verwijdering doorgaat. Je kunt je stem wijzigen door vóór de deadline op "
"de andere link te klikken.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

